screen_desc: The screenshot shows a mobile app login screen where users are prompted to enter their mobile number. The country code is set to Vietnam (+84) with a sample number entered. Below the mobile number input field, there is a "Continue" button. Alternative login options include "Continue with Google," "Continue with Apple," and "Continue with Email." There is also an option to "Find my account." At the bottom, there is a disclaimer about consent to receive calls and messages from Uber and its affiliates, and a note about the site being protected by reCAPTCHA along with links to the Google Privacy Policy and Terms of Service.
